      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS. This example boasts a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanically flawless, the rod bearings have been proactively addressed, and the rear subframe has been fully reinforced to ensure structural integrity under high-torque loads. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping with zero bushing deflection. This is a collector-quality specimen with a pristine undercarriage and a rev-happy 8,000 RPM redline.",
